title: 5 key takeaways from Jared Isaacman's 2nd NASA chief nomination hearing
description: Private billionaire SpaceX astronaut Jared Isaacman appeared before a Senate committee Dec. 3 for consideration as NASA administrator. Here are 5 big takeaways from the hearing.
